      "target_id": "sent_17_011",
      "target_type": "sentence",
      "task_id": "free_translation",
      "task_label_zh": "自由翻译",
      "task_label_en": "Free Translation",
      "value": "路上虽然遇到红灯，但我还是顺利回到家了。",
      "confidence": 0.9,
      "llm_used": true,
      "llm_name": "ChatGPT",
      "annotator_note": ""
    },
    {
      "annotation_id": "a_ft_22_001",
      "target_id": "sent_22_001",
      "target_type": "sentence",
      "task_id": "free_translation",
      "task_label_zh": "自由翻译",
      "task_label_en": "Free Translation",
      "value": "晚上十点时，我和刚失恋的朋友已经喝了不少酒。",
      "confidence": 0.88,
      "llm_used": true,
      "llm_name": "ChatGPT",
      "annotator_note": ""
    },
    {
      "annotation_id": "a_ft_22_002",
      "target_id": "sent_22_002",
      "target_type": "sentence",
      "task_id": "free_translation",
      "task_label_zh": "自由翻译",
      "task_label_en": "Free Translation",
      "value": "他喝醉后开始胡说八道，一会儿说爱的人不是那个男人而是我，一会儿又因为失恋哭，说自己心碎了还要看医生。",
      "confidence": 0.8,
      "llm_used": true,
      "llm_name": "ChatGPT",
      "annotator_note": ""
    },
    {
      "annotation_id": "a_ft_22_003",
      "target_id": "sent_22_003",
      "target_type": "sentence",
      "task_id": "free_translation",
      "task_label_zh": "自由翻译",
      "task_label_en": "Free Translation",
      "value": "我不让他再喝，但他还是喝过量，最后睡着了。",
      "confidence": 0.84,
      "llm_used": true,
      "llm_name": "ChatGPT",
      "annotator_note": ""
    },
    {
      "annotation_id": "a_ft_22_004",
      "target_id": "sent_22_004",
      "target_type": "sentence",
      "task_id": "free_translation",
      "task_label_zh": "自由翻译",
      "task_label_en": "Free Translation",
      "value": "我问他有没有钱，他说没有，于是我替他把账单付了。",
      "confidence": 0.86,
      "llm_used": true,
      "llm_name": "ChatGPT",
      "annotator_note": ""
    },
    {
      "annotation_id": "a_ft_22_005",
      "target_id": "sent_22_005",
      "target_type": "sentence",
      "task_id": "free_translation",
      "task_label_zh": "自由翻译",
      "task_label_en": "Free Translation",
      "value": "接着我叫了车，准备送他回家。",
      "confidence": 0.9,
      "llm_used": true,
      "llm_name": "ChatGPT",
      "annotator_note": ""
    },
    {
      "annotation_id": "a_ft_22_006",
      "target_id": "sent_22_006",
      "target_type": "sentence",
      "task_id": "free_translation",
      "task_label_zh": "自由翻译",
      "task_label_en": "Free Translation",
      "value": "到他家门口后，我按门铃，再用他的钥匙开门进去。",
      "confidence": 0.84,
      "llm_used": true,
      "llm_name": "ChatGPT",
      "annotator_note": ""
    },
    {
